                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18430508-1415-offence-1 t18430508-cd-18"></join>13th of April</rs>, 1/2lb. weight of tea, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18430508-name-155" type="victimName">
